{"tid":1437811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［社會實驗］你的新聞app如何，你的見解也必如何","createTime":"2019-08-09T15:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T11:11:13.000Z","uid":240030,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"29dad1c9d815bb8675d6ed84d166a3fbc74c6cb6","tid":1437811,"uid":240030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:34:10.000Z","msg":"［社會實驗］話說老竇睇完Yahoo新聞app，(Yahoo入面好多左報，啲留言區又好多藍絲洗版)，星期三同我講前線啲巴打收錢衝，即使同佢解釋冇人會肯收錢食咁多催淚彈都冇用⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n於是同我阿妹討論下點樣打救老竇，佢醒起之前登上有個巴打unlike哂自己老母個fb啲藍page，再like返啲健康page，好似立場、有線咁，一星期後好似話伯母由藍變黃，睇落幾work咁(2樓)<br />\n<br />\n忽發奇想之下，我哋就將老竇個Yahoo app刪咗，裝咗Now新聞，為免被發現好似好核突咁，我再將個Now app嘅logo粗粗地改做Yahoo個logo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2日之後嘅今晚，我老竇問我阿妹：「啲過期催淚彈呢，有咩害㗎」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tEyNWjB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtEyNWjB.gif&h=abedf161&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(Android幾易改，其實ios都得，有教學：<a href=\"https://applealmond.com/posts/48718\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapplealmond.com%2Fposts%2F48718&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrHs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=cb114b83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://applealmond.com/posts/48718</a>)"},{"pid":"1bb8a42b37517d5fdae1ecd3515e3b1029acd361","tid":1437811,"uid":240030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:34:51.000Z","msg":"[社會實驗]啱啱我同老母講，話佢部電話要更新<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1261946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1261946</a>"},{"pid":"327a88e0c782d0a086188392ae0d66afc0d593ba","tid":1437811,"uid":61697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:36:22.000Z","msg":"好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927dc17d08b94ee343f77edca73b746d132a0f50","tid":1437811,"uid":248670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019